      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Ahithophel is among the conspirators with Absalom; Absalom sent for him, and it seems he came to him, and continued with him, see 2 Samuel 15:12, ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "Ahithophel is among the conspirators with Absalom; Absalom sent for him, and it seems he came to him, and continued with him, see ",
